><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Feb 11, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jjg1665702536276.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jjg1665702536276.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jjg1665702536276.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jjg1665702536276\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Removes the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.Occurrence</span> object on the client.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"jjg1665702536276__topic_d126050e1_d126051e1_d126052e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jjg1665702536276__p_d126053e1_d126054e1_d126055e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">OccurrenceObject</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">.<span class=\"keyword apiname\">discard()</span>;</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jjg1665702536276__section_fmv_hbs_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d510460e67\">Arguments</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jjg1665702536276__section_ekf_3bs_bwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d510460e76\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jjg1665702536276__p_d126065e1_d126066e1_d126067e1\">Calling <span class=\"keyword apiname\">discard</span> on an occurrence\n        immediately removes the occurrence on the client, as well as all occurrences of the entities\n        that it contains. They no longer participate in subsequent requests to the server.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jjg1665702536276__p_d126068e1_d126069e1_d126070e1\">After this function is called, this Occurrence is no\n        longer valid, so many of its functions will throw a\n          <span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.InvalidDataObjectException</span>.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"jjg1665702536276__note_x1b_lbs_bwb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> This function does not mark the occurrence for\n        deletion on the server; you can use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">remove()</span> for that.</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/shk1665703139073.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.InvalidDataObjectException</a><p>Exception thrown if the object on which the function is called is no longer valid.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vkr1665703143808.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>remove()</a><p>Deletes the uniface.Occurrence object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hfh1665702535808.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Occurrence</a><p>The uniface.Occurrence object provides access to selected properties of the occurrence that it represents. It is returned by the getOccurrence function of the uniface.Entity object.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528904\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528904\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "discard Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Feb 11, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Removes the uniface.Occurrence object on the client. OccurrenceObject . discard() ; Arguments None Description Calling discard on an occurrence immediately removes the occurrence on the client, as well as all occurrences of the entities that it contains. They no longer participate in subsequent requests to the server. After this function is called, this Occurrence is no longer valid, so many of its functions will throw a uniface.InvalidDataObjectException . Note: This function does not mark the occurrence for deletion on the server; you can use the remove() for that. Related Links uniface.InvalidDataObjectException Exception thrown if the object on which the function is called is no longer valid. remove() Deletes the uniface.Occurrence object. uniface.Occurrence The uniface.Occurrence object provides access to selected properties of the occurrence that it represents. It is returned by the getOccurrence function of the uniface.Entity object. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}